---
import SectionContainer from "@/components/SectionContainer.astro";
---

<section class="philosophy-section">
  <div class="philosophy-wrapper">
    <!-- Header con quote destacado -->
    <div class="section-quote">
      <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
      <h2 class="quote-text">
        Bueno para tu casa,<br />
        bueno para el planeta
      </h2>
      <p class="quote-attribution">
        En LUFE, trabajamos desde el sincero convencimiento de que trabajar con
        madera maciza natural es la mejor decisión posible para amueblar con
        estilo y sostenibilidad.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Layout tipo revista con sidebar -->
    <div class="content-layout">

      <div class="content-main">
        <!-- Primer bloque de texto -->
        <div class="text-block block-featured">
          <p class="text-paragraph large">
            Los árboles crecen según el azar que dicta la naturaleza. Basta un
            breve paseo por un bosque para comprobar que no hay dos árboles
            iguales.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Grid de párrafos -->
        <div class="paragraphs-grid">
          <div class="paragraph-card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M12 2L2 7V13C2 19.05 6.29 24.25 12 25.5C17.71 24.25 22 19.05 22 13V7L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-paragraph">
              La madera es un producto vivo y natural. Y con sus nudos
              imperfectos y sus vetas de formas abstractas...es uno de los
              materiales más bellos que existen.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="paragraph-card">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M20 7H4M20 7L16 3M20 7L16 11M4 17H20M4 17L8 13M4 17L8 21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-paragraph">
              Y de hacerlo de forma sostenible, siendo respetuosos con nuestro
              entorno y con el planeta.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bloque destacado -->
        <div class="highlight-block">
          <p class="highlight-text">Pero no solo bello.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Texto continuo -->
        <div class="text-flow">
          <p class="text-paragraph">
            Por eso en LUFE estamos tan orgullosos de diseñar y fabricar
            muebles de madera de verdad que cualquiera se pueda permitir pero
            que no tengan un diseño cualquiera.
          </p>
          <p class="text-paragraph">
            Desde 2014 que se creó la marca, no hemos parado de diseñar pero
            tampoco de cortar, lijar o martillear.
          </p>
          <p class="text-paragraph">
            En LUFE nos manchamos de serrín cada día y esperamos que así siga
            siendo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Firma del fundador -->
        <div class="founder-signature">
          <div class="signature-content">
            <div class="signature-text">
              <p class="founder-name">Hector Vega</p>
              <p class="founder-title">Fundador de ARM Corporation</p>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-image">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1633265486064-086b219458ec?w=300&h=150&fit=crop&q=80"
                alt="Firma de Hector Vega"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .philosophy-section {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .philosophy-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5rem;
  }

  /* Section Quote */
  .section-quote {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    font-size: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: -3rem;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .quote-attribution {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Content Layout */
  .content-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .content-sidebar {
    position: relative;
  }

  .sidebar-sticky {
    position: sticky;
    top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sidebar-number {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.2;
    line-height: 1;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .sidebar-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-secondary), transparent);
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  .sidebar-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    text-orientation: mixed;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  /* Content Main */
  .content-main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  /* Text Block Featured */
  .text-block {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-secondary);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
  }

  .text-paragraph {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.15rem);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .text-paragraph.large {
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Paragraphs Grid */
  .paragraphs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .paragraph-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .paragraph-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  /* Highlight Block */
  .highlight-block {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .highlight-text {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  /* Text Flow */
  .text-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Founder Signature */
  .founder-signature {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .signature-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .signature-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .founder-name {
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .founder-title {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .signature-image {
    width: 200px;
    height: auto;
  }

  .signature-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.8;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .philosophy-section {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .philosophy-wrapper {
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    .content-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .sidebar-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .sidebar-line {
      height: 60px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .philosophy-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .philosophy-wrapper {
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .section-quote {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .content-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .content-sidebar {
      display: none;
    }

    .content-main {
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .text-block {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .paragraphs-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .paragraph-card {
      padding: 1.75rem;
    }

    .highlight-block {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .founder-signature {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .signature-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .signature-image {
      width: 180px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .philosophy-section {
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .philosophy-wrapper {
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .section-quote {
      padding: 1.5rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .quote-mark {
      font-size: 5rem;
      margin-bottom: -2rem;
    }

    .quote-text {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .quote-attribution {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .content-main {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .text-block {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-left-width: 3px;
    }

    .paragraph-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card-icon {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
    }

    .card-icon svg {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
    }

    .highlight-block {
      padding: 2rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .text-flow {
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .founder-signature {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .signature-content {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .founder-name {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .founder-title {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .signature-image {
      width: 150px;
    }
  }
</style>